Medical outcomes study social support survey (MOS-SSS) in patients with chronic 
disease: A psychometric assessment.

Merino-Soto C(1), Núñez Benítez MÁ(2), Domínguez-Guedea MT(3), Toledano-Toledano 
F(4)(5)(6), Moral de la Rubia J(7), Astudillo-García CI(8), Rivera-Rivera L(9), 
