Plain Language Summary of Publication of the safety and efficacy of ARRY-371797 
in people with dilated cardiomyopathy and a faulty LMNA gene.

MacRae CA(1), Taylor MR(2), Mestroni L(3), Moses J(3), Ashley EA(4), Wheeler 
MT(4), Lakdawala NK(1), Hershberger RE(5), Sandor V(6), Saunders ME(6), Oliver 
C(6), Lee PA(6), Judge DP(7).

Author information:
